        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-midnight-ink:#0a0a0a;--color-obsidian-slate:#262626;--color-deep-graphite:#353535;--color-electric-green:#27f795;--color-pure-white:#ffffff;--color-silver-mist:#8d8d8d;--font-roboto:'Roboto',system-ui,sans-serif;--font-roboto-mono:'Roboto Mono',monospace; background:var(--color-midnight-ink);padding:40px 24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:24px;width:600px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:12px;color:var(--color-silver-mist);margin:0;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;\">Use Cases</p><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;border:1px solid var(--color-deep-graphite);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;\"><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto-mono);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-silver-mist);background:transparent;padding:6px 12px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.0840em;border-right:1px solid var(--color-deep-graphite);display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;\">[SaaS / Dashboards]</a><span style=\"color:var(--color-deep-graphite);padding:0 2px;font-family:var(--font-roboto-mono);font-size:13px;\"></span><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto-mono);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-silver-mist);background:transparent;padding:6px 12px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.0840em;border-right:1px solid var(--color-deep-graphite);display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;\">[Observability]</a><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto-mono);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-silver-mist);background:transparent;padding:6px 12px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.0840em;border-right:1px solid var(--color-deep-graphite);display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;\">[AI Analytics]</a><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto-mono);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-silver-mist);background:transparent;padding:6px 12px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.0840em;border-right:1px solid var(--color-deep-graphite);display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;\">[Crypto / Finance]</a><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto-mono);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-electric-green);background:transparent;padding:6px 12px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.0840em;border:none;display:inline-block;white-space:nowrap;\">[Real-Time Analytics]</a></div></div>",
          "name": "Use Case Tag Selector",
          "role": "",
          "description": ""
        },
        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-midnight-ink:#0a0a0a;--color-obsidian-slate:#262626;--color-deep-graphite:#353535;--color-electric-green:#27f795;--color-pure-white:#ffffff;--color-silver-mist:#8d8d8d;--font-roboto:'Roboto',system-ui,sans-serif;--font-roboto-mono:'Roboto Mono',monospace; background:var(--color-midnight-ink);padding:40px 24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;width:600px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:8px;\"><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:16px;color:var(--color-silver-mist);margin:0;line-height:1.57;\">Hear why Tinybird is essential analytics infrastructure for modern software teams.</p></div><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;\"><div style=\"background:var(--color-obsidian-slate);border-radius:8px;padding:20px;\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--color-deep-graphite);flex-shrink:0;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b87333,#c8965a);\"></div></div><div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-pure-white);margin:0;line-height:1.3;\">Marc Lou</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:12px;color:var(--color-silver-mist);margin:0;line-height:1.5;\">Solopreneur</p></div></div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-pure-white);margin:0;line-height:1.6;\">I finally migrated DataFast's database to @tinybirdco and... HOLY SHIT IT'S F FAST! If you're a DataFast user, you can now enjoy much faster analytics.</p></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-obsidian-slate);border-radius:8px;padding:20px;\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--color-deep-graphite);flex-shrink:0;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4a6fa5,#6b8cba);\"></div></div><div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-pure-white);margin:0;line-height:1.3;\">Zeno Rocha</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:12px;color:var(--color-silver-mist);margin:0;line-height:1.5;\">Co-Founder & CEO at Resend</p></div></div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-pure-white);margin:0;line-height:1.6;\">Tinybird is exactly what we need it to be: infrastructure and tooling to ship analytics features. It eliminated what would have otherwise been a complex infra project.</p></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-obsidian-slate);border-radius:8px;padding:20px;\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--color-deep-graphite);flex-shrink:0;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2d7a4f,#47a36d);\"></div></div><div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-pure-white);margin:0;line-height:1.3;\">Jarred Palmer</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:12px;color:var(--color-silver-mist);margin:0;line-height:1.5;\">VP of AI at Vercel</p></div></div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-pure-white);margin:0;line-height:1.6;\">Tinybird's event ingestion endpoint is game changing. Instead of using Kafka or SNS, just send analytics events over HTTP — at up to 1000 req/sec.</p></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-obsidian-slate);border-radius:8px;padding:20px;\"><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--color-deep-graphite);flex-shrink:0;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7a4f2d,#a36d47);\"></div></div><div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-pure-white);margin:0;line-height:1.3;\">Marc González</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:12px;color:var(--color-silver-mist);margin:0;line-height:1.5;\">Director of Data at Factorial</p></div></div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto);font-size:13px;color:var(--color-pure-white);margin:0;line-height:1.6;\">We've shipped 12 new user-facing dashboards in just a few months. There's no way we could have done this without Tinybird.</p></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:16px;margin-top:8px;\"><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto-mono);font-size:14px;color:var(--color-midnight-ink);background:var(--color-electric-green);padding:10px 24px;border-radius:0px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.0840em;\">Join our Slack community</a><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-roboto-mono);font-size:14px;color:var(--color-electric-green);background:transparent;padding:10px 0;border-radius:0px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.0840em;\">Check out our GitHub</a></div></div>",
